rexml is an XML processor for the language Ruby.
rexml is conformant (passes 100% of the Oasis non-validating tests),
and includes full XPath support.
It is reasonably fast, and is implemented in pure Ruby.
Best of all, it has a clean, intuitive API.
This software is distribute under the Ruby license."

